for not protecting Aunt?

67
00:03:56,080 --> 00:03:56,710
Your Majesty.

68
00:03:56,710 --> 00:03:58,080
I don’t mean that.

69
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:02,190
My mother regarded you

70
00:04:02,520 --> 00:04:05,360
as her own son.

71
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:06,520
