than being awkward like this.

230
00:14:09,790 --> 00:14:10,960
I certainly know that.

231
00:14:13,750 --> 00:14:15,120
But I keep something from her

232
00:14:16,550 --> 00:14:17,720
just to protect her.

233
00:14:18,600 --> 00:14:19,510
